---
title: "Build Order — Phased Delivery"
---
gantt
    title FloxBot Build Phases
    dateFormat YYYY-MM-DD
    axisFormat %b %Y

    section Phase 1: Foundation
        Central API skeleton               :p1a, 2026-03-15, 3w
        Canon ingest pipeline              :p1b, 2026-03-15, 2w
        RAG retrieval (pgvector)           :p1c, after p1b, 2w
        CLI adapter                        :p1d, after p1a, 2w
        FloxHub auth integration           :p1e, after p1a, 1w
        Vote collection (store only)       :p1f, after p1d, 1w

    section Phase 2: Co-Pilot + Entitlements
        Co-Pilot env (ask/chat/diagnose)   :p2a, after p1f, 3w
        Entitlement gate                   :p2b, after p1e, 2w
        Local canon sync                   :p2c, after p2a, 2w
        Local memory persistence           :p2d, after p2a, 1w
        Offline vote/feedback queuing      :p2e, after p2d, 1w

    section Phase 3: Multi-Channel
        Slack adapter (Socket Mode)        :p3a, after p2b, 3w
        Discord adapter (Gateway)          :p3b, after p3a, 2w
        Email adapter (SendGrid)           :p3c, after p3b, 2w
        Cross-channel identity             :p3d, after p3a, 2w
        Intercom escalation bridge         :p3e, after p3d, 2w
        L1/L2 classification               :p3f, after p3a, 1w

    section Phase 4: Intelligence
        Codex integration                  :p4a, after p3f, 2w
        Skill detection engine             :p4b, after p3f, 3w
        Dynamic skill loading              :p4c, after p4b, 2w
        User memory (Tier 1)               :p4d, after p4a, 2w
        Instance knowledge (Tier 2)        :p4e, after p4d, 2w
        MCP server (flox ops)              :p4f, after p4a, 2w

    section Phase 5: Streaming + Feedback
        Kafka event backbone               :p5a, after p4c, 3w
        Flink: vote aggregation            :p5b, after p5a, 2w
        Flink: cross-channel correlation   :p5c, after p5b, 2w
        Flink: canon gaps + trending       :p5d, after p5c, 2w
        Field feedback pipeline            :p5e, after p5a, 2w
        Triaged tickets (copilot-ticket)   :p5f, after p5e, 1w
        Co-pilot learn mode                :p5g, after p5f, 3w

    section Phase 6: Enterprise
        Org knowledge layer                :p6a, after p5g, 3w
        Custom skill packages              :p6b, after p5g, 2w
        SSO integration                    :p6c, after p6a, 2w
        Admin dashboard                    :p6d, after p6a, 3w
        Priority escalation + SLA          :p6e, after p6c, 2w
        Environment telemetry              :p6f, after p6d, 2w
